## 2. User Accounts & Authentication

This website allows users to sign in using third-party services, specifically **GitHub**.

- **Data Collection**: When you sign in via GitHub, we may collect basic information such as your username, email address, and profile picture as provided by GitHub's OAuth service.
- **Responsibility**: You are responsible for maintaining the security of your GitHub account. Any actions taken through your authenticated session are your responsibility.
- **No Password Storage**: We do not store your GitHub password; authentication is handled entirely by GitHub.
- **Account Deletion**: If you wish to delete your account and all associated data, please send a request to [contact@tsuzat.com](mailto:contact@tsuzat.com). We will process your request within a reasonable timeframe.

